                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Ambassador <persName type="from">Griscom</persName> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.—Extract.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Petropolis</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1906-11-15">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 15, 1906</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Reports that he has been assured that the present tariff, including duty on
                    flour, will not be altered by this Congress, which expires December 31, and says
                    that the existing preferential list is almost certain to be continued for next
                    year.)</p>
            </div>
